Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥飛翔在  蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋倒映著  天空的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫中天空的藍色  是天空的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫中天空的藍色  是天空的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚的蔚藍中  小鳥在飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  把人生比作一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所處於的初中生階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是清晨天濛濛亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好短
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麼  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個好漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能做出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單  是織出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是普通的鎖鏈花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖鏈花樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種顏色的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  優
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得小鳥遊是種什麼遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小鳥腳上綁上一根細繩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣讓它飛起來  就像氣球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想聽你說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別鬧彆扭了  真透同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學才不是你說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  鎖鏈花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很適合紅色的  因為很白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你講日語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  你是想跟那個叫小鳥遊的交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個挺有趣的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有說有笑  表情千變萬化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  媽媽叫你去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽叫你洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}（繽紛小鳥  繽紛色彩）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小我就很嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帶我前往五彩繽紛的世界的小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(285,335)\fsp0}KOTORIASOBI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊…同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(310,335)\fsp0}TAKANASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀作無老鷹  寫成小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(384,335)\fsp0}KOTORIASOBI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(290,335)\fsp0}TAKANASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會讀成無老鷹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小鳥遊玩的地方沒有老鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名字起得好聰明！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請  請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊要參加什麼社團  決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也討厭整天這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭整天黏著她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝霞輔導室？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要加點砂糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師沒跟你說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩惱可以來這裡傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是心理醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了初中自然而然就會有煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎  沒啥感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有煩惱  那就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有事想談談的時候就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是來喝咖啡也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  速度加快些  再快些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是體驗入社  一上來就快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學都是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來是繞東海道跑一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我跑出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜上所述  每人畫兩張速寫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先每兩人組成一組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交替著做模特兒來相互作畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太拼命了  吐一下會好點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太會怎麼吐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來還有應募經理人的說明會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯簡單點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別  咖哩的話我就吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉…嗯  咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「繽紛小鳥  繽紛色彩」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  繽紛小鳥的待機桌布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個上哪裡找的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我自己畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也對  繪本裡沒有這張畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你那本不是初版的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初版裡有這張畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  封面是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是嗎  我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初版  在我家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  快夠地方打籃球了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真的很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的話就送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再做一條就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  是小篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  是黃泉幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黃泉幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗  瑪卡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這個茶色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爛泥色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅色的給黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝要紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒顏色的都給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個  不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好精緻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕上的奶油還有花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  梅亞里  這人打算待到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是篝說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅亞里說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咖哩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要露出那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  給我那些瑪卡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做錯什麼事了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.88,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,140)\fs15}小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.88,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,238)\fs15}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉是篝的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好負起責任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
