Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道車站前的神社有個祭典活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的女生好些人都約好了  說要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得去的話一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  真的不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在一起的時候總覺得不會說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去告白不就好了  小潘同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有說的那麼簡單  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和老師一樣胸部有那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潘…前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密啊  沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  那麼快就有煩惱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得被討厭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你是黑衣同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從一開始見到你就這麼覺得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙眼瞳大概從沒有厭惡別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從沒有被別人討厭過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意不豎立敵對關係是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  人們總是在不知不覺之中樹敵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  不管是誰都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受這樣的理所當然就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算胸口就像被刺穿一樣疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會噴出鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會傷口化膿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人替你承受這份疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多疼痛即使受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正受傷的人一定不是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  要多加點砂糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人替我承受這份疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別留得太晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想和我成為朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭…祭典…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的真的不會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…去看五彩繽紛的萬物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五彩…繽紛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繽紛的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋倒映著…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫中天空的藍色…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天空的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚的蔚藍中…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥在飛翔
